{
  "_comment": "Ryazhenka Updater download catalogue. URL shapes understood by source/list_download_tab.cpp: (1) direct https URLs for assets with a stable filename; (2) '@latest_asset:OWNER/REPO' — resolved at click time via api.github.com, takes the first asset matching the content type's preferred extension (.zip for archives, .bin for payloads/hekate_ipl), fallback assets[0]; (3) '@download_to:<DEST>:<URL_or_marker>' — single-file download to DEST, no extract, for .ovl / .nro; (4) '@reorg_ppsspp:OWNER/REPO' — like @latest_asset then moves PPSSPP_GL.nro to /switch/ and assets/ to /switch/ppsspp/. NOTE: direct releases/latest/download/<name> aliases only work when the asset filename is version-free; Atmosphere and hekate embed the version, so they MUST use @latest_asset.",
